    <div class="article comment" id="cid-1583537">
      <p class="text">I too have many happy memories of eating Lefse in Ames Iowa with my grandmother and her sisters. Hot black coffee and lefse - spread with cold butter and sprinkled sugar... there is nothing like it.</p>
      <div class="footer meta">
